Queen Nwokoye" (amuru na 11 August n'afọ 1982) bu nwa ada naijiria nke na eme ihe nkiri na ónyonyò. Akacha amaraya maka na ono na ime ihe nkiri nke obu onye isi na ndi otu ka ha so mee ihe egwuregwu na ime 2014 nke ana akpo Chetanna.
Queen bu onye amuru na obodo Lagos State na ime ezi na ulo Catholic ma na obu onye Anambra State
Oguchara akwukwo sekondiri na Queen's College, nke di na Enugu tupu owee gawa mahadum nke Nnamdi Azikiwe ebe nke ono wee guo akwukwo ana akpo 'Sociology and Anthropology'
Obu uzo buru na obi ka ogu akwụkwọ ima iwu nke ana akpo onye ikpe.

ke mgbe oguchara egwu na afo 2004 na ime ihe onyonyo nke ana kpo Nna Men, Queen garaniru ibu onye gbara na ime otutu ihe nkiri egwu nke ndi Naijiria,nke oji otutu itu ugo na nhoputa maka itu ugo.< ref>Chidumga Izuzu (11 August 2015)
Queen Nwokoye: ihe ise Ana anya ị maghị maka onye na-eme ihe nkiri
